HR 391 Original 2026 Regular Session Martinez
Creates the 18th Judicial District Drug Court and Behavioral Health Services Task Force to
study the effectiveness and outcomes of the 18th Judicial District Court Drug Court
Program. Requires the task force to submit a written report of its findings and
recommendations to the respective legislative committees no later than Feb. 1, 2027.
